T10:45:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fc7d3244a7cfa554f974f86749ed8cb0e554b8c","tid":37561,"uid":41037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f4a04378876599f5fa344ef36edd90b4dfb57f91","tid":37561,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:30:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"273b30d5234c3ea8a4b265e49d132c730988fa5f","tid":37561,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:34:53.000Z","msg":"我都想知咩鏡一淋就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我支FE1635 去旅行淋過幾次都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5610b93fd9ff62e11e1905d222c8fe690f1dd5ff","tid":37561,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜唔係正常情況咩？光線暗，曝光過度（EV、ISO、曝光時間），所以會出現種光柱</blockquote><br />\n又係你呀師兄<br />\n唔係用開電話影咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用我影既相做例子，呢種光柱根本係正常情況，夜攝光線不足，暗位過暗，拉高暗位亮度結果令光位過光，就有呢種情況。我懷疑菲林唔會有呢種情況，之前我個帖某位巴扛話乜野CMOS dynamic range闊，係啊，真係好闊，結果咪光位爆光，暗位過暗，闊得好緊要。反而dynamic range窄的菲林唔會有呢種情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161106_232854_vHDR_Auto.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d6Wh8LJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd6Wh8LJ.jpg&h=f8e25aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161106_233103_vHDR_Auto.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eaRniZb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeaRniZb.jpg&h=c29d988c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161106_233302_vHDR_Auto.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WsckHKt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWsckHKt.jpg&h=0355db5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161117_040745_SRES.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b4/P_20161117_040745_SRES.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb4%2FP_20161117_040745_SRES.jpg&h=8f693ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161117_040948_vHDR_Auto.jpg，呢張係HDR auto，估計已經開左HDR，將曝光過度（拉高暗位）同曝光不足（拉低光位）合併，都仲係咁，有光柱：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/11wFp1m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F11wFp1m.jpg&h=95d08ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_020015_NT.jpg，開左夜間模式：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YFzQs3R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYFzQs3R.jpg&h=6d9d67c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實係鏡片coating問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707da8514fc79a511f51194a2bc0c97b2e514c89","tid":37561,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想知咩鏡一淋就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我支FE1635 去旅行淋過幾次都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有機身加鏡頭無防水果類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79009839a09fcc629189da222818a91324b1e80","tid":37561,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e662ec37180291ebd4249dd1fa43f308f8381361","tid":37561,"uid":35216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"岩先屎忽痕，為左睇下係咪coating問題，我拎左部手機(htc10) 同廢單反去試，睇睇光柱呢個炫光問題因素點控制到<br />\n手機我已經揾左最ok 無咩耀光果張了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0axofmy4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0axofmy4&h=779e7d6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n手機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/k74f6x9r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fk74f6x9r&h=29a01f0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單反with 1680 我都知舊機燥點多，張就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我覺得係睇鏡片有無落足料，無就耀光好勁"},{"pid":"0b7982a2cc5bb30db075a57362d0d3906e634aef","tid":37561,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:26:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ae4fc69c3a68a200127584c9db1a9f9fb49c4e4","tid":37561,"uid":7378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔關coating（鏡片保護膜）事<br />\n<br />\n較低ISO、曝光時間（快門時間）、同EV（曝光值），就唔會有光柱同光位爆光問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以示範下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50bee0a827faf758db985234dba3fadec4e33550","tid":37561,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都想知咩鏡一淋就壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我支FE1635 去旅行淋過幾次都無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所有機身加鏡頭無防水果類<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上次大帽山零度結冰，拎D700+Sigma 2470無防水<br />\n部機何止淋雨，直頭冰封，連變焦環都凍死左轉唔到<br />\n然後到依家都係運作正常"},{"pid":"3327fb0367d9eaf7de1073ce686dc70f2a4b9c7d","tid":37561,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d6f3e3115869888bbea303fa1101d16c4c549da","tid":37561,"uid":7378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:02:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔關coating（鏡片保護膜）事<br />\n<br />\n較低ISO、曝光時間（快門時間）、同EV（曝光值），就唔會有光柱同光位爆光問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以示範下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢三張相，正常曝光係會睇唔到塊藍底白字路牌的字，因為光位爆光。將ISO、曝光時間（快門時間）、EV較到最低就會睇到，但暗位完全暗到睇唔到。ISO、曝光時間（快門時間）、EV第一張最低，第二張中間，第三張最高：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_210309.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3dIaqXk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3dIaqXk.jpg&h=ebc9e431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_210447.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/glUtg7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FglUtg7P.jpg&h=28134bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_210712.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vgTzDCN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvgTzDCN.jpg&h=9da0471c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正常曝光係會睇唔到IFC左下同右下廣告牌的字，因為光位爆光：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_220959_SRES.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/us3sQwQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fus3sQwQ.jpg&h=a539ed7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_221100_SRES.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NtK2RET.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNtK2RET.jpg&h=aa34f86b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將ISO、曝光時間（快門時間）、EV較到最低就會睇到，但暗位完全暗到睇唔到。ISO、曝光時間（快門時間）、EV第一張高少少，第二張低d，留意到第二張IFC左下同右下廣告牌的字清d，左下有「Season's Greeting」同「Manulife」，右下有「AIA」同「中」：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_223200.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8tHVUJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8tHVUJK.jpg&h=b7f4c0fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP_20161213_223249.jpg<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wYspzE0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwYspzE0.jpg&h=cfcc65a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n菲林唔會有呢種光位爆光，暗位過暗的情況，維基百科講法係寬容度高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你只係show咗你部手機dynamic range有幾低畀大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLens flare點樣解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪張張相黑媽媽就叫無lens flare, 因為係一點光都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc07a5e36466a7da46b8b437e0a6479411108cc4","tid":37561,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bc893db2205b5841f2b539d67957c3a8c234816","tid":37561,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f80b3ea0ee4958c23fec86e64dfc5c841fc3fb0d","tid":37561,"uid":7378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你只係show咗你部手機dynamic range有幾低畀大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nLens flare點樣解決？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪張張相黑媽媽就叫無lens flare, 因為係一點光都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你真係冇乜慧根，<span style=\"color: red;\">冇錯，較低ISO、Shutter speed、EV，雖然黑蚊蚊，但確實解決左光位爆光同光柱的問題！！！</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我之前講左，菲林機光位爆光，暗位過暗的問題冇CMOS咁嚴重</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利用曝光不足去避免爆光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁點解唔正正經經影Raw, 正確曝光再返去用lightroom拉返低光位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fcd2c6516a7c036cbeed03fd490193b44ea65b","tid":37561,"uid":7378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>光位爆光，暗位過暗、運動模糊等現像，CMOS嚴重過肉眼同菲林，所以低速運動既物體，明明肉眼－視網膜同菲林成像好清，但CMOS朦查查，如果較低CMOS的Shutter speed，又會入光不足好暗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你有無用過單反或者無反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家既單反無反cmos dynamic range都已經12,13EVS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相同參數下，點會cmos會模糊，菲林唔會呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8512e119f0517a1a9eebdc5d7bbf5858726ff78","tid":37561,"uid":29141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:50:48.000Z","msg":"係咪假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3870be857702fc1dce8cc510a077bd2b32818df6","tid":37561,"uid":64451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"我想問影到光柱巴打係咪都有用filter? 我經驗係9成9除左filter就無左fog鏡/flare。除非支鏡真係廢到無倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecc3ab3de0d3dc51523e9b70251c70e2672a599f","tid":37561,"uid":18516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>光位爆光，暗位過暗、運動模糊等現像，CMOS嚴重過肉眼同菲林，所以低速運動既物體，明明肉眼－視網膜同菲林成像好清，但CMOS朦查查，如果較低CMOS的Shutter speed，又會入光不足好暗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你有無用過單反或者無反？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家既單反無反cmos dynamic range都已經12,13EVS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相同參數下，點會cmos會模糊，菲林唔會呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢條友根本冇用過相機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上個post吹奏菲林<br />\n點知原來自己冇用過菲林<br />\n俾啲新手睇到學錯野就慘"}]}